THIRD-PARTY IMAGES (NOT COVERED BY THE MIT LICENSE ABOVE)

The MIT license above covers the source code of this project only. It does NOT
cover the book cover images and author portraits displayed on the site.

Those images are fetched at build time from third-party sources — book covers
from Open Library (https://openlibrary.org/) and author portraits from Wikimedia
Commons (https://commons.wikimedia.org/) — and are the property of their
respective rights holders. They are used to identify the books the club reads.
They are not committed to this repository (the on-disk image cache under
`website/src/assets/images/` is gitignored and regenerated from those sources),
and they are not the author's to relicense. If you fork or reuse this project,
you are responsible for your own compliance with the terms of Open Library,
Wikimedia Commons, and the underlying rights holders for any images you fetch or
display.
